USB Connectors
--------------

There are 4 x Type A **USB HOST connectors** onboard, as shown on the figure below.

.. Figure:: /Media/ARM/A9/PPC_Others/USB.jpeg
  :align: center
  :figclass: align-center

  *USB HOST Connectors*

There is also 1 x Type Mini B **USB OTG connector**, configured as slave by
default.

.. Figure:: /Media/ARM/A9/PPC_Others/USB_OTG.jpeg
  :align: center
  :figclass: align-center

  *USB OTG Connector*

:pagebreak:`True`
